{"type":"message","id":"43e829da","parentId":"d5bcfc1d","timestamp":"2026-06-06T03:35:23.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是\"6.1 版本的数据存储结构是不是又升级了\"。这个问题比较模糊——\"6.1\"可能指：\n\n1. OpenClaw 6.1 版本\n2. 飞书某个 API 的 6.1 版本\n3. 用户自己业务的某个系统 6.1 版本\n4. 其他软件版本\n\n从上下文看，我（KIIT/大总管）维护的 MEMORY.md 里提到了 OpenClaw 2026.5.20 是当前 memory-core 版本，但没看到 6.1 相关的记录。\n\n我需要先：\n1. 检查 MEMORY.md 里的相关记录\n2. 看看最近的 memory 文件有没有相关线索\n3. 必要的话问一下用户具体指什么\n\n但其实最直接的——我应该先查一下 memory，看看是不是有 OpenClaw 6.1 升级的记录。如果没有相关记忆，应该问清楚是哪个系统的 6.1 版本。\n\n让我快速查一下 memory 文件。","thinkingSignature":"52f64e94222897c32e8763faa56f0ce23be81fd1c06571780051cdc3a9bf4f46"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jharxm1tar8h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ 2>/dev/null | tail -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jharxm1tar8h_2","name":"lcm_grep","arguments":{"pattern":"6\\.1|6\\.1\\.0|升级|升级.*数据|数据存储|version 6","mode":"regex","scope":"both","limit":20,"sort":"recency"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":52234,"output":332,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52680,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780716909282,"responseId":"0672c86e2f6d61c6db0a0ecc44f3ddf9"}}
