{"type":"message","id":"e36201db","parentId":"c27d6357","timestamp":"2026-06-06T08:35:19.354Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前确实是 OpenClaw 2026.6.1。我看到有 `openclaw.json.bak` 多个备份、`pre-update` 备份、还有 `restart-sentinel.json` 临时文件，这说明 6.1 是新升级上来的。\n\n让我快速查一下：\n1. 看看 `pre-update` 备份是什么时候的（确认升级时间）\n2. 看看 docs 里有没有 6.1 的 release notes\n3. 看看 `lcm.db` 和 `lcm.db-wal` - 这是 lancedb 还是 sqlite\n4. 看看 `state/` 目录结构\n\n用户问的\"数据存储结构\"具体指什么还不明确。OpenClaw 有多个存储层：\n- LCM (lcm.db, lcm-files)\n- memory (MEMORY.md + memory/)\n- state/\n- workspace/\n- skills/\n- agents/\n\n让我并行查一下 docs 和 release notes。","thinkingSignature":"ad6f5e1aab83e7b8da4136a17061eb3611b836d2530a97046dd20e765e119ba2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gu8qv38ghx2r_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/pre-restore-20260502-114822/ 2>/dev/null | head -10; echo \"---pre-update---\"; ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json.pre-update 2>/dev/null; echo \"---update-check---\"; cat /home/halei/.openclaw/update-check.json 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gu8qv38ghx2r_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/ 2>/dev/null | head -20; echo \"---\"; find /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/ -maxdepth 2 -name \"CHANGELOG*\" -o -name \"RELEASE*\" -o -name \"release-notes*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gu8qv38ghx2r_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/halei/.openclaw/state/ 2>/dev/null; echo \"---lcm-files---\"; ls /home/halei/.openclaw/lcm-files/ 2>/dev/null | head -20; echo \"---memory/ size---\"; du -sh /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ 2>/dev/null; du -sh /home/halei/.openclaw/lcm.db 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":346,"output":518,"cacheRead":54681,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55545,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cach