{"type":"message","id":"6669ea03","parentId":"b02e58e1","timestamp":"2026-06-06T08:43:53.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在确认上一条最后那句\"要不要我顺带查一下这个 sqlite 里有哪些表、迁移得干不干净？\"——他在问\"还升级了什么\"，他提到了\"skill 自我进化\"。\n\n让我从 CHANGELOG 里挑出 6.1 跟\"skill 自我进化\"相关的内容，以及其他他可能关心的升级。\n\n\"Skill 自我进化\"在 6.1 里对应的是 **Skill Workshop** —— 之前 CHANGELOG 里就有看到：\n- \"Skill Workshop now has a fuller Control UI flow with proposal lists, today actions, revision handoff, searchable file previews, review states, locale coverage, and reusable session routing.\"\n- \"Skills: let the `skill_workshop` agent tool apply, reject, and quarantine explicit proposals through the guarded review flow.\"\n- \"Skills: let proposals carry approved support files under standard skill folders, with scanner, hash, and rollback safeguards.\"\n- \"Skills: let pending proposals be revised in place with versioned, dated proposal frontmatter before approval.\"\n- \"Skills: add Skill Workshop with pending proposals, CLI/Gateway review actions, rollback metadata, and the `skill_workshop` agent tool.\"\n\n我自己的工具列表里就有 `skill_workshop` 工具 —— 这就是新加的\"skill 自我进化\"机制。\n\n但用户问的不只是 skill，还有\"别的吗\"——所以我应该：\n1. 先回答\"skill 自我进化\"是不是 6.1 新加的（是的，Skill Workshop）\n2. 再列其他重要升级（与业务相关、和 HALEI 团队相关）\n\n从 CHANGELOG 看我之前拉到的内容里还有：\n- **Workboard** 加了多 Agent 协调原语和工具 (#87469, #82326) - 我的工具列表里就有 workboard_* 这一整套\n- **Code mode** 加了内部命名空间\n- **Providers: add MiniMax M3 model support** (#88860) - 我们正在用！\n- **Memory: QMD 优化**\n- **Channels: 飞书优化** - 长 stream reply、可见 fallback、tolerate timestamp skew 等\n- **Chat/UI**: Dreaming tab agent selector (我们在用)\n- **Security/config parsing**: 拒绝不安全的 OAuth/token lifetime、retry-after、命令超时等\n\n我应该挑对 HALEI 团队最有用的来讲。\n\n另外用户也同意了\"查 sqlite 里有哪些表、迁移得干不干净\"——所以我也应该做这个。\n\n让我并行做：\n1. 查 sqlite 表结构\n2. 再 grep 一下 CHANGELOG 找更多相关变更\n\n实际上上一轮我已经 grep 过 .tables 没出来，可能 sqlite3 没装。让我先尝试一下别的方法。","thinkingSignature":"71392ea3df6dbe71da8c7034711fece13d88767b0447ecf4ad670d8c6d5e5b4d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nwldqsxt9l8e_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== sqlite3 是否可用 ===\"; which sqlite3; sqlite3 --version 2>&1 | head -1\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 试 node 读 sqlite schema ===\"\nnode -e \"\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst buf = fs.readFileSync('/home/halei/.openclaw/state/openclaw.sqlite');\nconst magic = buf.slice(0,16).toString('utf-8');\nconsole.log('magic:', JSON.stringify(magic.slice(0,6)));\n\" 2>&1\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 找系统里的 sqlite 工具 ===\"\nls /usr/bin/sqlite* /usr/local/bin/sqlite* 2>/dev/null\napt list --installed 2>/dev/null | grep -i sqlite | head -3\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 试 python ===\"\npython3 -c \"\nimport sqlite3\ncon = sqlite3.connect('/home/halei/.openclaw/state/openclaw.sqlite')\ncur = con.execute(\\\"SELECT name FROM sqlite_master WHERE type='table' ORDER BY name\\\")\ntables = [r[0] for r in cur.fetchall()]\nprint('tables:', tables)\nfor t in tables:\n    n = con.execute(f'SELECT COUNT(*) FROM \\\"{t}\\\"').fetchone()[0]\n    print(f'  {t}: {n} rows')\n\" 2>&1 | head -40"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nwldqsxt9l8e_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== grep CHANGELOG 找其他 HALEI 关心的升级点 ===\"\ngrep -nE \"Workboard|Code mode|Skill Workshop|MiniMax|Feishu|Memory:|Dreaming|provider.*M3|model.*M3|QMD|envelope|auth.*atomic|token lifetime|sandbox|email|gmail|msteams|microsoft\" /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/CHANGELOG.md 2>/dev/null | head -40\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 当前已安装 plugins ===\"\nls /home/halei/.openclaw/plugins/ 2>/dev/null\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 是否能看到 workboard 数据库 ===\"\nfind /home/halei/.openclaw -maxdepth 3 -name \"*.sqlite*\" 2>/dev/null\necho \"\"\necho \"=== lancedb 是否已装 ===\"\nls /home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/ 2>/dev/null\nfind /home/halei/.openclaw -maxdepth 4 -name \"*lance*\" -o -name \"*.lance\" 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1246,"output":1147,"cacheRead