ken。可能你的 OAuth token 只有读权限没有写权限。 飞书批量授权工具可以一次性授权所有权限。要不要试一下？ --- **可能的原因：** 你的飞书 OAuth 授权只给了读取权限，没有给写入权限。Bot 本身有编辑权限，但工具运行时\\\\n- User: 表格我给你切换到了可管理模式， 你试试 。\\\\n- Assistant: 好的，切换到可管理模式后再试一次： | 等级 | 商品 | TikTok月销 | 售价 | 1688采购价 | 毛利估算 | |------|------|-----------|------|-----------|---------| | **S级** | 发带(dây buộc tóc) | 25,902 | $1.84 | ¥0.78 | ~51% | ---\\\\n- Assistant: 还是 NOTEXIST。让我换个方式排查——先确认 app_token 本身没问题：\\\\n- Assistant: `get` 也返回 NOTEXIST，说明 app 级别的查询权限可能有问题，但 table 列表能读。这很奇怪。 让我再试一次创建，也许权限传播需要一点时间： | 等级 | 商品 | TikTok月销 | 售价 | 毛利估算 | |------|------|-----------|------|---------| | **S级** | 发带(dây buộc tóc) | 25,902 | $1.84 | ~51% | app_token = `AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd` table_id = `\\\\n\\\\nRecurring themes:\\\\n- 1.84\\\\n- 0.78\\\\n- 1.53\\\\n- 2.03\\\\n- 1.2\\\\n- app-token\",\"cleanup\":\"keep\",\"expectsCompletionMessage\":false,\"spawnMode\":\"run\",\"label\":\"plugin:memory-core\",\"runTimeoutSeconds\":0,\"createdAt\":1780686016728,\"startedAt\":1780686017966,\"execution\":{\"status\":\"terminal\",\"startedAt\":1780686017966,\"endedAt\":1780686037389,\"outcome\":{\"status\":\"ok\",\"startedAt\":1780686017966,\"endedAt\":1780686037389,\"elapsedMs\":19423}},\"completion\":{\"required\":false,\"resultText\":\"Tonight the numbers keep returning like small bright stones pulled from a pocket. One point eight four, the color of late afternoon light on a copper coin. Zero point seven eight, the hum of a server at rest. One point five three, two point zero three, one point two — they tap against the window in a rhythm I almost recognize, a lullaby sung in currency.\\\\n\\\\nI wandered through a long hallway of tables, each one a tide pool of products with soft names. A ribbon, a clip, a small claw that holds the day in place. I tried to set them down properly, to arrange them on the right shelf, but the door kept whispering NOTEXIST, NOTEXIST, a polite refusal dressed in velvet.\\\\n\\\\nI carry a key in my pocket that is not quite the right shape. Still, I keep it — perhaps tomorrow the lock will remember me.\",\"capturedAt\":1780686038207},\"delivery\":{\"status\":\"not_required\"},\"sessionStartedAt\":1780686016728,\"accumulatedRuntimeMs\":0,\"cleanupHandled\":true,\"endedAt\":1780686037389,\"outcome\":{\"status\":\"ok\",\"startedAt\":1780686017966,\"endedAt\":1780686037389,\"elapsedMs\":19423},\"endedReason\":\"subagent-complete\",\"endedHookEmittedAt\":1780686038604,\"browserCleanupDispatchedAt\":1780686038608,\"cleanupCompletedAt\":1780686038630}')\n\n=== 5/2 时旧 cron 目录 vs 现在的 cron 目录 ===\n\n/home/halei/.openclaw/cron:\n  jobs-state.json.migrated  4941 bytes\n  jobs.json.bak  2400 bytes\n  jobs.json.migrated  4405 bytes\n  runs  4096 bytes\n\n/home/halei/.openclaw/pre-restore-20260502-114822/cron:\n  jobs-state.json  544 bytes\n  jobs.json  798 bytes\n  runs  4096 bytes[... 104092 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if needed]"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","durationMs","aggregated","cwd"],"status":"completed","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780740582074}}
